OL,3,CDetectives given extension to question
OL,4,Cman in custody after car hits
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FPolice have been given an extension to
OL,8,Fquestion a man who is is custody after
OL,9,Fseven pedestrians were struck by a car
OL,10,Fin Derby on Saturday evening.
OL,12,FA 36-year-old man was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of attempted murder shortly
OL,14,Fafter the incident happened.
OL,16,FDerbyshire Police say they have until
OL,17,Ftomorrow evening to question the
OL,18,Fsuspect.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
