PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774980701
OL,3,CDetectives given extension to question
OL,4,Cman in custody after car hits
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FFour men and three women-aged between
OL,8,F36 and 52- were taken to hospital and
OL,9,Ftreated at the Derby Royal Hospital
OL,10,Fand the Queen's Medical Centre in
OL,11,FNottingham.
OL,13,FThey all sustained serious but not
OL,14,Flife-threatening injuries and three of
OL,15,Fthem have now been discharged from
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
