OL,3,CDetectives given extension to question
OL,4,Cman in custody after car hits
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Emma Aldred
OL,8,Fsaid:"I'd like to reiterate my well
OL,9,Fwishes to all the victims in this case
OL,10,Fas they begin their recovery supported
OL,11,Fby specialist officers.
OL,13,F"I also want to thank the eyewitnesses
OL,14,Fwhose reports allowed us to make an
OL,15,Farrest just minutes after this
OL,16,Fincident happened.
OL,26,@pD@FOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
