PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774980701
OL,3,CDetectives given extension to question
OL,4,Cman in custody after car hits
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"The response to this incident was a
OL,8,Fmulti-agency one and we are continuing
OL,9,Fto work closely with partners and
OL,10,Flocal businesses. I'd like to thank
OL,11,Fthem for all of their support.
OL,13,F"Detectives are continuing to question
OL,14,Fthe arrested man and have been
OL,15,Fcarrying out extensive enquiries over
OL,16,Fthe last couple of days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
