PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774980701
OL,3,CDetectives given extension to question
OL,4,Cman in custody after car hits
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"While I understand that there is
OL,8,Fsignificant interest in the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of this case, at this
OL,10,Ftime it is extremely important that we
OL,11,Fmaintain the integrity of the
OL,12,Finvestigation to ensure that it is as
OL,13,Fthorough and proportionate as the
OL,14,Fpublic would expect.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
